channel.title: Website Developer [ENSO-RS]
channel.description:
Hello.
I'm looking for a decent website developer that could handle the forum & main website. You can contact me by adding my skype: nexonltd
Enso is one of the most advanced private servers ever done, with very big amount of unique content. (Release date has been decided 5.7.2014)
Project media [img]http://puu.sh/9Lhb7/803a755581.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9KTB9/878068c98f.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9L1kH/9b772928e5.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9Jtlt/41adb6086d.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9NHHY/2e13ad3109.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9NHTP/4368d13e31.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9IukS/909ab328dc.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9Mi0F/7f61c886ac.jpg[/img]
Enso is a upcoming succesfull server, we are looking for over 2-3 website developers to work with.
